name: Walnut_Five-tiered_Corner_Bookcase
reviews: This is a nightmare to assemble!!!! Plus all of the pieces did not fit together properly! Angry that I can't return so I ended up throwing the entire item in the trash!

Not terribly difficult to assemble. The color is a VERY dark espresso, almost black. I was expecting a walnut color from the item listing. Too dark for the room I bought it for, but I'll find somewhere else to use it. It's cute, I like the style.
The bookshelves are very well made and interesting looking. A little wider than I thought. Didn't go in the small space, but I found another. Recommend carefully measuring for widest area.
exactly what we needed for a small entryway into our master bedroom
Not that easy to put together but it is nice.
Great addition for corner or small area.
It was a little frustrating putting together at first, but when we finally got the instructions straight. It was well worth it. I love the look it adds to my living room area.
description:
Store your hardcovers in modern style with this five-tiered corner
bookcase. Featuring a compact, bottle-shaped design, this bookcase
allows you to maximize space in an unused nook or create a stunning
focal point along a wall. Display photo frames, plants,
collectibles and other decorative items at eye level while placing
